{"tid":1396234,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"關於侵侵嘅言論，大家無需無限放大，自己香港自己救！！","createTime":"2019-08-02T04:30:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-02T06:48:45.000Z","uid":148783,"like":15,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"032d4bf0475a798d317060ffe30ba770ad6544a0","tid":1396234,"uid":148783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T04:30:27.000Z","msg":"其實唔知啲人有無睇曬全文<br />\n不過我覺得trump係回應緊上次港澳辦記者會同埋老懵董話有外國勢力嘅問題<br />\n佢意思係香港問題係應該由返香港同大陸去解決<br />\n屌 好撚正常啫<br />\n所以自己香港自己救 咪撚求人！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而家仲有好多抗爭運動進行緊<br />\n唔好比呢啲野轉移視線！！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">自己香港自己救！</span></span>"},{"pid":"b9a9e50e61c0c14086e5b058f34f20e192d7639e","tid":1396234,"uid":148783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T04:31:48.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">自己香港自己救！</span></span>"},{"pid":"3fcc9bcb31487fbb823137dd21ca0514b07b571f","tid":1396234,"uid":148783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T04:32:44.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">自己香港自己救！</span></span>"},{"pid":"4fbc5acf33bb3e01d517d219b10d8ffc4829f184","tid":1396234,"uid":257422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T04:33:09.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">我地可以迫大集團表態，<br />\n只要佢地肯表態唔反對，<br />\n市民自然會少左個包袱去罷工</span><br />\n<br />\n <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">一人一信 推到 大貓 今日內交代 8月5罷工 立場！！！！！</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1396162\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1396162</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1AMiNLW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1AMiNLW.jpg&h=611f7a48&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"314a3a169c71bf6d062626936fbe8139786e1676","tid":1396234,"uid":271962,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T04:34:38.000Z","msg":"根本就無理過 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a26f393d2d1254f68acbcdd884b7faf3b48f53e","tid":1396234,"uid":258696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T04:35:14.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"52dd004bf152c6fcb8c7eb3b0eb1275dfed89d78","tid":1396234,"uid":148783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T05:56:50.000Z","msg":"自己香港自己救！"},{"pid":"9f04d38437ad2672683b32e0c34a97806d43a51b","tid":1396234,"uid":148783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T05:59:19.000Z","msg":"自己香港自己救！"},{"pid":"143df1aaf043a3730ed353fddce1555bc9a9e61b","tid":1396234,"uid":195570,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T06:02:32.000Z","msg":"侵侵老奸巨滑，無著數點會攬上身"},{"pid":"faddf4ddf46af34ed89f5b801f9e1e1e390cc1a6","tid":1396234,"uid":245078,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T06:05:45.000Z","msg":"等佢打貿易戰消耗中國經濟就夠，其他野洗咩佢幫手，而且佢係唔會做無錢賺既野"},{"pid":"926f6ba2b70a660c559f19f1afe4719b6938fe07","tid":1396234,"uid":148783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T06:29:27.000Z","msg":"自己香港自己救！"},{"pid":"cacbd79029fe06ffbf4748d865be559166464a19","tid":1396234,"uid":148783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"143df1aaf043a3730ed353fddce1555bc9a9e61b","tid":1396234,"uid":195570,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T06:02:32.000Z","msg":"侵侵老奸巨滑，無著數點會攬上身"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T06:30:22.000Z","msg":"已經夠 搞到支那內憂外患已經夠"},{"pid":"bb94548363c87b109a542a64d4710340abb72122","tid":1396234,"uid":6528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T06:33:47.000Z","msg":"全民8月5日大罷工！五大訴求，缺一不可！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n雙普選一定要排最頭，仲要好似美國咁設時限係2020年之前落實<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n全民黑衫、口罩同頭盔，返工返學行街，唔擺工既日子一齊做，將抗爭帶入生活，保護示威者<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1379839\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1379839</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n當新移民夠多，雙普選自然會落實，港共明顯會用偽民主反真港人<br />\n（雖然係舊post，但都想人諗下，一定要止左血先）<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1328467\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1328467</a><br />\n<br />\n光復香港，時代革命！<br />\n－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－<br />\n想比更多人知道其實而家呢一刻基本上得番<span style=\"color: gold;\">香港獨立</span>呢條路，<br />\n我知好多人未準備好，我知而家急唔黎。<br />\n但係想大家思考下，種下一個思想，唔好屌我住。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n而家就算有真普選其實都係under中共！！<br />\n咁唔通去到2047再抗爭過咩，西方國家都出唔到手幫你地。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n因為白紙黑字寫明50年，西方國家唔好話出手，連發聲既正當性都冇啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n可能好多前人都係到諗點解英國當時唔寫999年！<br />\n可能好多我地呢代既諗點解上一代冇去抗爭！<br />\n可能好多下一代係2047係到諗點解我地唔直接爭取獨立！！！<br />\n<br />\n我地唔可以好似上一代咁，計好哂數50年後都死左啦，唔好理啦。<br />\n我地唔可以再咁自私啦，過埋2047都嗰頭近啦，之後再算啦。<br />\n我想我地既下一代唔需要再為呢啲事再受苦啦，我只係希望下一代可以係呼吸住自由既空氣出世係呢個地球上。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n所有既問題，所有既恩怨，係我地呢代到解決哂啦，好嗎？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所有問題去到最後只會追究到主權問題，希望大家思考下。<br />\n今次搞到咁大真係最後一次反擊同最大力量。<br />\n<br />\nBTW，五大訴求，缺一不可！<br />\n雙普選應要排最頭，仲要設時限，最好2020年之前！"},{"pid":"f2ec95503594d47187ce67ad0598db8dfaf9389b","tid":1396234,"uid":148783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T06:44:05.000Z","msg":"自己香港自己救！"},{"pid":"fab0617aba7230877623dcfac9ece824fa4f1025","tid":1396234,"uid":60321,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T06:47:26.000Z","msg":"其實我地問題源自中共/中國 佢專心直接搞死中共已經好好"},{"pid":"d874ae2c046685752e23e2b744c12642f20fff59","tid":1396234,"uid":169043,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T06:48:45.000Z","msg":"自己香港自己救"}]}